game_select_category_description_kpvp_10: Battle as a team of three to capture altars and siege the enemy nexus in this fast-paced game mode.
game_select_category_description_kpvp_11: Use a randomly selected champion to crush your lane, dive into epic five-on-five team fights, and destroy the enemy nexus.
Choose your favorite Assassin and hunt your way to victory in this Featured Game Mode.
Crush your lane, dive into epic five-on-five team fights, and destroy the enemy nexus in League's premier competitive mode.
Battle with friends against the Doom Bots of Doom and their evil overlord in this fast survival style game mode.
Take turns attacking and defending the Nexus using unique and powerful Siege Weapons. How fast can you destroy the enemy nexus!?
Play as a random champion and fire off your abilities nonstop in this Ultra-Rapid game mode.
game_select_category_description_kpvp_12: Ten randomly-selected champions assemble on a narrow bridge in a frozen land. Cross to the other side and destroy everything in your path.
Throw Poros at each other, summon the legendary Poro King, then feed him snax to push together to victory.
Portals have been unleashed upon the Howling Abyss! Ride them together as you push to victory.
game_select_category_description_kpvp_16: Play as Thresh and feed souls to the Dark Star to trigger the Singularity in this quick, round-based 3v3 mode set on the Cosmic Ruins.
game_select_category_description_kpvp_18: Fight together as Star Guardians against the invading monsters to save the city in this 5 player co-op battle!
game_select_category_description_kpvp_8_: Battle for awe-inspiring power in this intense 5v5 brawl. Who will Ascend?!
Work with your allies to seize capture points and declare dominion over your enemies.
game_select_category_description_ktraini: Learn more advanced techniques in an instructional Summoner's Rift game.
Practice your favorite champion in this 1-10 player Summoner's Rift training gym!
Learn the basics in this instructive tutorial flow.
Learn the basics in this instructive tutorial map.
game_select_category_description_kversus: Team up with other players against a team of bots and destroy the enemy Nexus.
Team up with other players against a team of bots and destroy the enemy Nexus.
Battle with friends against the Doom Bots of Doom and their evil overlord in this fast survival style game mode.
Team up with other players against a team of bots and destroy the enemy Nexus.
Team up with other players against a team of bots and destroy the enemy Nexus.
game_select_category_description_kpvp_11: Authentic SR gameplay in a much shorter match. Play with friends of different skill levels without the fear of falling too far behind.
game_select_category_description_kpvp_22: Assemble a team of champions to battle it out in an 8-player free-for-all. Any strategy goes, but only one can win.
Climb the ladder from Iron to Challenger using your wits and creativity against other Ranked players.
Think fast! This rapid-fire mode is high-risk, high-reward, with simpler econ so you can focus on teambuilding.
Reinforce your partner with back-up, trade items, send champs, and gift loot to become the last duo standing!
Choncc's feeling generous! Start with a powerful champion and get showered with loot in this chaotic game mode.
In this timerless PvE mode, plan out new strategies at your own pace within TFT's current set.
These sets are even better the second time! Set revivals also feature unique playstyle-based progression - the Revival Ladder.
Dragons are back in the Convergence! Earn rewards through the Revival Ladder by playing this limited-time game mode.
Celebrate Lunar Revel with a themed, limited-time game mode and festive holiday rewards.
Come celebrate Pengu's birthday bash in this limited-time game mode with your favorite traits from past sets.
Team up with a Guide and go on a solo timerless PvE adventure to climb the mountain!

tft_playbook_tutorial_paragraph_body_1: Before starting your game, you can pick a Legend that offers Legend-specific Augments in your preferred playstyle.
tft_playbook_tutorial_paragraph_body_2: Legends support a playstyle and not a specific team comp. Your first of each three Augment choices will always come from your Legend, but each Augment can be individually rerolled if you need something else to fit your team.
tft_playbook_tutorial_paragraph_body_3: Don't have a favorite yet? Pick "Poro" to play with the standard pool of Augments.
tft_playbook_tutorial_body:
Before starting TFT in any mode, you can choose a Legend, which provides access to a unique set of augments.

One of your augments in-game will always contain an option from your Legend!

Don't have a favorite yet? Pick "Poro" to play with the standard pool of augments.
tft_playbook_cta_body: Make sure to choose your favorite option before starting the next game.

role_swap_ftux_card_jungle_description: Jungle players will be auto-assigned the Smite spell. Only one Smite allowed per team.
role_swap_ftux_card_support_description$:
Once in game, Support players will be auto-assigned the World Atlas support item.

Supports will be highly incentivized to spend the lane phase in bot lane.
role_swap_ftux_card_role_swapping_descri:
We've added the ability to swap roles in Champ Select.

This gives you the opportunity to trade with willing teammates.
